name: Kiyomizudera in Winter
description:
A rare view of heavy snow at Kiyomizudera Temple in Kyoto. 
For this edition, I am going to send you the printed picture as a Postcard as a bonus straight from Japan! 
If your country is not reachable from here, I am going to send you the hi-res file. 
Only 3 Postcards are going to be given, so only the first hand buyer are eligible to receive it.
